{"sn35.99:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.99 ","sn35.99:0.2":"10. Salavagga ","sn35.99:0.3":"Samadhisutta ","sn35.99:1.1":"“Samadhim, bhikkhave, bhavetha. ","sn35.99:1.2":"Samahito, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathabhutam pajanati. ","sn35.99:1.3":"Kinca yathabhutam pajanati? ","sn35.99:1.4":"‘Cakkhu aniccan’ti yathabhutam pajanati; ","sn35.99:1.5":"‘rupa anicca’ti yathabhutam pajanati; ","sn35.99:1.6":"‘cakkhuvinnanam aniccan’ti yathabhutam pajanati; ","sn35.99:1.7":"‘cakkhusamphasso anicco’ti yathabhutam pajanati. ","sn35.99:1.8":"‘Yampidam cakkhusamphassapaccaya uppajjati vedayitam sukham va dukkham va adukkhamasukham va tampi aniccan’ti yathabhutam pajanati …pe… ","sn35.99:1.9":"‘mano aniccan’ti yathabhutam pajanati. ","sn35.99:1.10":"Dhamma … ","sn35.99:1.11":"manovinnanam … ","sn35.99:1.12":"manosamphasso … ","sn35.99:1.13":"‘yampidam manosamphassapaccaya uppajjati vedayitam sukham va dukkham va adukkhamasukham va tampi aniccan’ti yathabhutam pajanati. ","sn35.99:1.14":"Samadhim, bhikkhave, bhavetha. ","sn35.99:1.15":"Samahito, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yathabhutam pajanati”ti. ","sn35.99:1.16":"Chattham. "}